flowRoot.flowPara: Base of the policy confguration objects:
- Groups: dynamic of static groups of nodes
- Rules: policy defined by a set of directive, applied
- Node properties: external data for a node, used
to contextualize policies for that node
- Network: card interfaces, IPs, mask, etc
Used to update dynamic groups membership
